You're currently trying to draw a segmented progress arc similar to your `SegmentedProgressIndicator2` directly in the `SimpleTextWidgetProvider`. Let's adapt your current progress indicator to work in a standard widget:

```kotlin:app/src/main/java/com/devrachit/ken/widget/SimpleTextWidgetProvider.kt
package com.devrachit.ken.widget

import android.annotation.SuppressLint
import android.appwidget.AppWidgetManager
import android.appwidget.AppWidgetProvider
import android.content.Context
