Let's add a network error dialog to your OnboardingFragment that appears when there's no internet connection. Since you already have a `NetworkStateObserver` and a `NetworkErrorDialog` composable, we can integrate these:

```kotlin:app/src/main/java/com/devrachit/ken/presentation/screens/auth/onboarding/OnboardingFragment.kt
