 window.statusBarColor = bgColor
 window.navigationBarColor = bgColor
 }
}
```

This update:

1. Replaces the deprecated direct setting of `statusBarColor` and `navigationBarColor` with the modern approach
2. Uses `WindowInsetsControllerCompat` to control the appearance of both status bar and navigation bar
3. Makes the status and navigation bars transparent on Android 10+ (API 29+) for true edge-to-edge
4. Provides a fallback for older versions to maintain compatibility
5. Maintains the light/dark appearance setting

This approach is more in line with modern Android development practices and handles edge-to-edge properly while avoiding deprecated APIs."}]}

