You're getting the error "Suspension functions can only be called within coroutine body" because `suspendCoroutine` is a suspension function, and you're trying to call `withContext` (another suspension function) directly from within it. Here's how to fix it:

```kotlin:app/src/main/java/com/devrachit/ken/presentation/screens/auth/onboarding/OnboardingViewmodel.kt
private suspend fun checkIfUserExistsOnLeetCode(username: String): Boolean {
 // The GraphQL query to check if a user exists - fixed format
 val query = """
 {
 "query": "query { matchedUser(username: \\"$username\\") { username } }",
 "variables": {}
 }
 """.trimIndent()

